These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
City: miami, venice
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, tulip
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| City   | venice    | miami |
| Flower         | tulip | amaryllis    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, action
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the canadian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Movie-Genre      | action  | drama   |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian  |
| Hobby     | fishing   | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
City: hamburg, liverpool
House: craftsman, palace
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| City         | hamburg   | liverpool  |
| House   | palace | craftsman  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

