.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Hobby    | skydiving | chess     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Birthday   | december | march    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-8::.
