.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, techno
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, handball
1. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | techno  |
| Sport     | handball | volleyball    |

 